graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	commonGetAttachmentLibraries (query: $query)

		id
		name
		path
		filename
		url
		mime
		extension
		size
		width
		height
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

}
